data.description: Step into this remarkably well-lit home, complete with vaulted ceilings, sky lights, and a south facing sunroom, perfect for sun-loving foliage. Easy to clean, durable ceramic tile floors and classic hardwood throughout all the high-traffic areas of the home, with cozy carpet in each bedroom and loft office space (used as 4th bedroom). The exterior buildings feature the ever-important multi-vehicle garage with RV space. Storage upon storage! Above garage is an unfinished studio, plumbed with bathroom and shower. In addition, the chicken coop and rabbit hutches are built on-site. This property has irrigation access for all of your gardening needs. Century-old trees and creek access provides a sense of tranquility to the back of the property.
